  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/e881c76d3eac488ad9d5ff6ade03634a.poster.avif?t=1734424211\" width=780 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/e881c76d3eac488ad9d5ff6ade03634a.webm?t=1734424211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/e881c76d3eac488ad9d5ff6ade03634a.mp4?t=1734424211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We invite you to plunge into the world of puzzles, prepared for you - Sudoku 9X16X25. The rules are simple - fill in the grid by digits in such a way that they do not repeat horizontally, vertically and in the nearest square. Also, you can complicate or simplify the game by changing the numbers to letters or symbols.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game have different sizes, difficulty levels and a huge number of puzzles, especially for those who are not afraid of difficult tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Under quiet music and pleasant game design, you can brighten up your leisure time and develop your logic skills.   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/10dc27da17af2a51d33626f5885688f7.poster.avif?t=1734424211\" width=780 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/10dc27da17af2a51d33626f5885688f7.webm?t=1734424211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/10dc27da17af2a51d33626f5885688f7.mp4?t=1734424211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The size of the playing field: 9х9; 16х16; 25х25</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ability to change numbers to letters or symbols</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficulty settings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >150 puzzles for each size (9х9; 16х16; 25х25)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >User mode. Random level generator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >User-friendly design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make notes opportunity</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saving level progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are settings: music volume and screen resolution</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/e881c76d3eac488ad9d5ff6ade03634a.poster.avif?t=1734424211\" width=780 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/e881c76d3eac488ad9d5ff6ade03634a.webm?t=1734424211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/e881c76d3eac488ad9d5ff6ade03634a.mp4?t=1734424211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We invite you to plunge into the world of puzzles, prepared for you - Sudoku 9X16X25. The rules are simple - fill in the grid by digits in such a way that they do not repeat horizontally, vertically and in the nearest square. Also, you can complicate or simplify the game by changing the numbers to letters or symbols.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game have different sizes, difficulty levels and a huge number of puzzles, especially for those who are not afraid of difficult tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Under quiet music and pleasant game design, you can brighten up your leisure time and develop your logic skills.   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/10dc27da17af2a51d33626f5885688f7.poster.avif?t=1734424211\" width=780 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/10dc27da17af2a51d33626f5885688f7.webm?t=1734424211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1089880/extras/10dc27da17af2a51d33626f5885688f7.mp4?t=1734424211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The size of the playing field: 9х9; 16х16; 25х25</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ability to change numbers to letters or symbols</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficulty settings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >150 puzzles for each size (9х9; 16х16; 25х25)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >User mode. Random level generator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >User-friendly design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make notes opportunity</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saving level progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are settings: music volume and screen resolution</p></li></ul>",
